data.description: Discover your dream retreat in this 3-bed, 2.5-bath haven with a stunning backyard view of a serene lake. Wake up to birdsong and wildlife, complemented by a golf course across the street. Upgrades in 2022 include a new HVAC, generator, and luxury flooring. The newer metal roof, granite counters, vinyl windows, and composite decking add modern charm. Ample storage and more await inside. Located in Fairfield Bay, a Greers Ferry Lake resort town, this property provides access to over 100 miles of hiking/ATV trails, two PGA golf courses, three swimming pools, mini-golf, bowling, and more. Make this your home, where nature meets luxury and resort living is at your doorstep!
